snippet: Eight states on the East and West coasts released a plan Thursday for working together to put 3.3 million zero-emission vehicles on the nation's roads by 2025....

headline.print_headline: 8 States Release Action Plan to Promote Clean Cars
headline.main: 8 States Release Action Plan to Promote Clean Cars

lead_paragraph: Eight states on the East and West coasts released a plan Thursday for working together to put 3.3 million zero-emission vehicles on the nation's roads by 2025.
